Our Wall Street doctor's office is on the corner of Exchange Place and Broad Street. We are directly one block south of the NYSE and "My Suit" Men's Clothing is the street-level storefront of 30 Broad. Please bring a photo ID and allow additional time to check in with the security desk.

Parking

The closest lot is Modern Parking at 666 Fifth Avenue (entrance is located at 20 W 53rd Street, between 5th and 6th Avenues). Rates start at $15 for 30 minutes. Street parking is very limited.

Additional Information

Our Midtown - E 53rd St doctor's office is at 515 Madison at East 53rd, right next to Essen Market. The entrance to the building is on the 53rd Street directly next to the E/M subway entrance. Please allow for extra time to check in at the security desk in the lobby.

Bikes are permitted in the building, and patients can park their bikes in the back near the bathrooms.

Parking

There are parking lots at 85 W 15th Street ($43 for the first hour) and 222 W 14th Street ($34/hour).

Additional Information

Our doctor's office on West 14th Street is on the SW side of the block, diagonally across from the Apple store and next door to Lululemon. Our West 14th Street doctor's office is just one block from the Chelsea Market. Patients should buzz 'One Medical Group' from the outside door to be let in and then take the elevator to the 2nd floor. Please note that once you’ve buzzed in, a green light will appear on the intercom to indicate that the door is now open.

Unfortunately bikes are not allowed inside the building at this time, but bike racks outside are available.
